Package com.intellij.openapi.editor.ex.util

Class IntBasedStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.editor.ex.util.IntBasedStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataStorage

    public class IntBasedStorage
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataStorage
    SegmentArrayWithData storage based on the int array. It allows to store one int per segment. It allows to pack IElementType index and state of the lexer for segment.
